<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/326345-i-will-probably-be-tempted-to-compare">I will probably be tempted to compare &quot;Terre des Hommes&quot; to &quot;Le Petit Prince&quot;. As the latter is an extremelly tough piece to follow, will this ruin the whole experience for me or should I regard &quot;Terre des Hommes&quot; as an entirely different spiritual quest?</a>
